4 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
5 Sec. 1. CHARTER ADOPTION APPROVAL
6 The General Assembly approves the adoption of the charter of the Town of
7 Morristown as set forth in this act. The voters of the Town approved the
8 proposal of adoption on November 5, 2024.
9 Sec. 2. REDESIGNATION
10 24 App. V.S.A. chapter 129C (Town of Northfield) is redesignated to
11 24 App. V.S.A. chapter 129D.
12 Sec. 3. 24 App. V.S.A. chapter 129C is added to read:
13 CHAPTER 129C. TOWN OF MORRISTOWN
14 § 1. CORPORATE EXISTENCE RETAINED
15 The inhabitants of the Town of Morristown, within the corporate limits now
16 established, shall continue to be a municipal corporation by the name of the
17 Town of Morristown.
18 § 2. GENERAL LAW; APPLICATION
19 Except when changed or modified by this charter, or by any lawful
20 regulation or ordinance of the Town, all of the statutes of the State relating to
21 municipalities shall apply to the Town.
